data.title: 2010 Fair Market Rent in Coffee County
data.meta_description: FY 2010 Fair Market Rent for Coffee County, TN. Fair Market Rent for a two-bedroom home in Coffee County is $582 per month.
data.text:
Fair Market Rent prices in Coffee County are average compared to the national average. This FMR area is more expensive than 54% of other FMR areas. Fair Market Rent for a two-bedroom apartment in Coffee County is $582 per month.

The previous year, rent for a two-bedroom home was $563 per month. This is a 3.37% increase year-over-year.

This FMR rate applies to Summitville, TN, Arnold Afb, TN, Hillsboro, TN, Estill Springs, TN, Manchester, TN and other cities within the region. The Metro Code or CBSA code for this region is NCNTY47031N47031.

Additionally, This Fair Market Rent (FMR) area Coffee County, TN spans one county or city in Tennessee which is listed in the table below. Estimated population of Coffee County, TN FMR area is 48,014 people based on latest Census data.

Compared to the rest of Tennessee, the Coffee County FMR area is more expensive than 84% of the state.
